{
  "stem": "13238.2",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "It was a quite well-known story in the city of Krakow.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "By then we were sent out to the airport, my brother and myself, by the end of 1942.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "They were building barracks for a few hundred workers at the airport.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And my father said to us, look, I hope you'll be able to survive.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "I had an aunt and an uncle.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "They were childless.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "They loved my little sister very much.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "So my father said the auntie would take care of her.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "You go over there because you have a better chance to survive.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "But we never knew, as he joined, already, the underground in the city of Krakow.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "He disappeared from ghetto in 1942.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "I never saw my father again.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "Like I said before, he was a very strong man.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "I never met such a strong man in my lifetime.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "He could do anything.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "Naturally, as a young man, in your father you see always the giant of the man, but he was.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "And what he did, he did because he couldn't live by himself, not to avenge his wife.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "What I heard, he was in the city preparing all kinds of bombs underground.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "They were throwing on different section.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "One of them is a famous place, they called it the Nightclub [?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "Sigonaria, ?] where the Germans used to come to enjoy themselves.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "He was one of the men who would throw the bomb on the [?",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "Sigonaria ?] Nightclub.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "And many, many other things, what people were telling me because I didn't know anything about it.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "What I find out later on, in the beginning, in February, in 1943, he was arrested, was thrown into a jail of Gestapo.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "They used to call it Montelupi-- was a terrible, terrible jail.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
